---
const pains = [
  'Disconnected systems',
  'Manual workflows',
  'Transaction failures',
  'Slow approvals',
  'Messy customer operations',
  'Weak automation',
  'Poor visibility',
  'Products that do not scale',
];
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="shell">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.95fr_1.05fr] lg:gap-16">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow mb-5">The real problem</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl leading-tight sm:text-4xl">
          Most digital transformation fails because it ignores execution.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-5 text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted">
        <p>
          Most companies do not have a technology problem alone. They have an
          <span class="text-fg"> execution problem</span>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Their teams deal with disconnected systems, manual workflows, transaction failures, slow
          approvals, messy customer operations, weak automation, poor visibility, and products that
          do not scale.
        </p>
        <p class="text-fg">
          Technoliberals helps companies convert these operational problems into clear product
          roadmaps, AI-enabled workflows, and production-grade digital systems.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <ul class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-2 gap-px overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-line bg-line sm:grid-cols-4">
      {
        pains.map((pain) => (
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-ink px-5 py-5 text-sm text-muted">
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-muted-2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.3 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.7 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.4 0Z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
            {pain}
          </li>
        ))
      }
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
